#: addons/Maps_from_Teayo.wad/addon:6 input:6 standard
msgid ""
"This Addon contains all of my Maps. Some of my Maps are also on the "
"Widelands Website Maps archive aviable. Maps Total : 25 , Major Maps : 9 , "
"Variant Maps : 15 , Major Maps with Variant Maps : 5"
msgstr ""
"Aquest complement conté tots els meus mapes. Alguns dels meus mapes també es "
"troben a l'arxiu de mapes del lloc web de Widelands disponible. Total de "
"mapes : 25 , mapes principals : 9 , mapes variant : 15 , mapes principals "
"amb mapes variant : 5"

#: addons/Maps_from_Teayo.wad/addon:9 input:9 standard
msgid "Maps_from_Teayo"
msgstr "Mapes de Teayo"

#: addons/Maps_from_Teayo.wad/dirnames:4 standard input:4
msgid "Teayo's Karten"
msgstr "Mapes de Teayo"

#: input:3 screenshots/Maps_from_Teayo.wad/descriptions:3 standard
msgid "A Overview of the Map Circle Island in Editor"
msgstr "Una vista del mapa «Illa Circular» a l'editor"

#: input:4 screenshots/Maps_from_Teayo.wad/descriptions:4 standard
msgid "A Overview of the Map Lack of Space in Editor"
msgstr "Una vista del mapa «Falta d'Espai» a l'editor"

#: input:5 screenshots/Maps_from_Teayo.wad/descriptions:5 standard
msgid "A Overview of the Map Lack of Space 2 in Editor"
msgstr "Una vista del mapa «Falta d'Espai 2» a l'editor"

#: input:6 screenshots/Maps_from_Teayo.wad/descriptions:6 standard
msgid "A Overview of the Map Rectangle Valley Variant 1 in Editor"
msgstr "Una visió general de la Variant 1 de Map Rectangle Valley a l'Editor"

#: input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"A circular island with a large mountain in the middle. Eight valleys run "
"through the edges of the mountain. Large stone deposits are in the valleys. "
"A sparse forest covers the entire remaining area of ​​the island. There is a "
"lot of wildlife. Harbors can be built on the island's beach."
msgstr ""
"Una illa circular amb una gran muntanya al mig. Vuit valls travessen les "
"vores de la muntanya. A les valls hi ha grans dipòsits de pedra. Un bosc "
"escàs cobreix tota l'àrea restant de l'illa. Hi ha molta fauna. Es poden "
"construir ports a la platja de l'illa."

#: input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"A multiplayer map designed for short rounds. Whoever builds the best economy "
"fastest has the best chance of conquering the whole island. Artifacts are "
"scattered around the outskirts of the island. On the mountain, in the middle "
"of the island, there is a large building site. For example a castle. All raw "
"materials are available in limited quantities. This Map is also on Widelands "
"Website Map archive aviable. Map archive Meta (2023-07-06) : [ Upload : "
"2021-10-27 , Downloads : 392 , Comments : 0 , Rating : 0 (0 Votes) , Last "
"Edit : [ 2023-07-06 , Widelands-Version 1.2 , Map Edit : Translated the Map "
"Title, Description and Hint from german into english. ] ]"
msgstr ""
"Un mapa multijugador dissenyat per a rondes curtes. Qui construeix la millor "
"economia més ràpid té les millors possibilitats de conquerir tota l'illa. "
"Els artefactes estan escampats pels afores de l'illa. A la muntanya, al mig "
"de l'illa, hi ha una gran obra. Per exemple un castell. Totes les matèries "
"primeres estan disponibles en quantitats limitades. Aquest mapa també es "
"troba disponible a l'arxiu de mapes del lloc web de Widelands. Arxiu de "
"mapes Meta (2023-07-06): [ Upload : 2021-10-27 , Downloads : 392 , "
"Comments : 0 , Rating : 0 (0 Votes) , Last Edit : [ 2023-07-06 , Widelands-"
"Version 1.2 , Map Edit : Translated the Map Title, Description and Hint from "
"german into english. ] ]"

#: input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"A symmetrical green square valley surrounded by resource-rich mountains. Two "
"small forests and rock formations are present in balanced quantities at the "
"two starting positions. Rivers with fish are present in the valley. This map "
"is designed for multiplayer duels. For short rounds, but for players who "
"want to have a short preparation time in the form of a short distance buffer "
"to the opponent. There is a maximum of building space in the entire valley. "
"Water is only available near rivers! There are 5 artifacts in total, all "
"distributed along the Valley Center axis. This Map is also on Widelands "
"Website Map archive aviable. Map archive Meta (2023-07-06) : [ Upload : "
"2021-10-24 , Downloads : 344 , Comments : 0 , Rating : 0 (0 Votes) , Last "
"Edit : [ 2023-07-06 , Widelands Version 1.2 , Map Edit : Translated the Map "
"Title, Description and Hint from german into english. ] ]"
msgstr ""
"Una vall quadrada verda simètrica envoltada de muntanyes riques en recursos. "
"Dos petits boscos i formacions rocoses estan presents en quantitats "
"equilibrades a les dues posicions inicials. A la vall hi ha rius amb peixos. "
"Aquest mapa està dissenyat per a duels multijugador. Per a rondes curtes, "
"però per a jugadors que volen disposar d'un temps de preparació curt en "
"forma d'amortidor de distància curta a l'oponent. Hi ha un màxim d'espai "
"edificable a tota la vall. Només hi ha aigua a prop dels rius! Hi ha 5 "
"artefactes en total, tots distribuïts al llarg de l'eix Valley Center. "
"Aquest mapa també es troba disponible a l'arxiu de mapes del lloc web de "
"Widelands. Arxiu de mapes Meta (2023-07-06): [ Upload : 2021-10-24 , "
"Downloads : 344 , Comments : 0 , Rating : 0 (0 Votes) , Last Edit : "
"[ 2023-07-06 , Widelands Version 1.2 , Map Edit : Translated the Map Title, "
"Description and Hint from german into english. ] ]"

#: input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"A very small, symmetrical valley with adequate forest, rock formations, "
"fish, and ore resources. The map is designed for multiplayer. Designed for "
"short to very short rounds, there is no prep distance buffer between the two "
"players. This Map is also on Widelands Website Map archive aviable. Map "
"archive Meta (2023-07-06) : [ Upload : 2020-07-23 , Downloads : 352 , "
"Comments : 0 , Rating : 6 (2 Votes) , Last Edit : [ 2023-07-06 , Widelands "
"Version 1.2 , Map Edit : Translated the Map Title, Description and Hint from "
"german into english. ] ]"
msgstr ""
"Una vall molt petita i simètrica amb un bosc adequat, formacions rocoses, "
"peixos i recursos minerals. El mapa està dissenyat per a multijugador. "
"Dissenyat per a rondes curtes a molt curtes, no hi ha un buffer de distància "
"de preparació entre els dos jugadors. Aquest mapa també es troba disponible "
"a l'arxiu de mapes del lloc web de Widelands. Arxiu de mapes Meta "
"(2023-07-06): [ Upload : 2020-07-23 , Downloads : 352 , Comments : 0 , "
"Rating : 6 (2 Votes) , Last Edit : [ 2023-07-06 , Widelands Version 1.2 , "
"Map Edit : Translated the Map Title, Description and Hint from german into "
"english. ] ]"

#: input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"Eight islands in the middle of the ocean. Each island has six harbor "
"building sites, one harbor building site in each corner of the island. All "
"islands are the same size and arranged evenly, so that the distance between "
"the individual islands is as equal as possible. The starting position is in "
"the middle of the island and due to its proximity to the coast, it is hardly "
"protected from landings. Each island is sufficiently large and therefore "
"offers sufficient building space."
msgstr ""
"Vuit illes al mig de l'oceà. Cada illa té sis llocs de construcció del port, "
"un lloc de construcció del port a cada racó de l'illa. Totes les illes tenen "
"la mateixa mida i estan disposades de manera uniforme, de manera que la "
"distància entre les illes individuals sigui el més igual possible. La "
"posició de partida és al mig de l'illa i per la seva proximitat a la costa, "
"gairebé no està protegida dels desembarcaments. Cada illa és prou gran i, "
"per tant, ofereix prou espai d'edificació."

#: input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"Eine Vorlage Karte ohne Spieler und mit Raster auf einen Ozean. Eine gute "
"Grundlage um eine symetrische, ausgewogene Karte darauf aufbauend zu "
"erstellen."
msgstr ""

#: input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"Fight against seven other opponents with minimal resources and minimal "
"building space. All resources are sufficiently available at the start. This "
"Map is also on Widelands Website Map archive aviable. Map archive Meta "
"(2023-07-06) : [ Upload : 2020-07-19 , Downloads : 422 , Comments : 0 , "
"Rating : 4.67 (3 Votes) , Last Edit : [ 2023-07-06 , Widelands-Version 1.2 , "
"Map Edit : Translated the Map Title, Description and Hint from german into "
"english. Remastered Resources Amount, Position and Count of Trees and "
"Rocks. ] ]"
msgstr ""
"Lluita contra altres set oponents amb recursos mínims i espai de construcció "
"mínim. Tots els recursos estan prou disponibles al principi. Aquest mapa "
"també es troba disponible a l'arxiu de mapes del lloc web de Widelands. "
"Arxiu de mapes Meta (2023-07-06): [ Upload : 2020-07-19 , Downloads : 422 , "
"Comments : 0 , Rating : 4.67 (3 Votes) , Last Edit : [ 2023-07-06 , "
"Widelands-Version 1.2 , Map Edit : Translated the Map Title, Description and "
"Hint from german into english. Remastered Resources Amount, Position and "
"Count of Trees and Rocks. ] ]"

#: input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
